<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>星双</title><link>https://jzjizhe.github.io/</link><description>Recent content on 星双</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 06 Sep 2025 23:23:21 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://jzjizhe.github.io/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>推导两个一维正态分布的KL散度</title><link>https://jzjizhe.github.io/theory/%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%B4%E6%AD%A3%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84kl%E6%95%A3%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 06 Sep 2025 23:23:21 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://jzjizhe.github.io/theory/%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%B4%E6%AD%A3%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84kl%E6%95%A3%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>&lt;p>设&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
P(x) \sim \mathcal{N}(\mu_1, \sigma_1^2), \quad Q(x) \sim \mathcal{N}(\mu_2, \sigma_2^2)&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>定义&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
D_{\mathrm{KL}}(P|Q) = \int P(x) \log \frac{P(x)}{Q(x)} , dx&lt;br>
$$&lt;br>
则有&lt;br>
$$&lt;br>
\boxed{&lt;br>
D_{\mathrm{KL}}(P|Q) = \ln \frac{\sigma_2}{\sigma_1}&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>\frac{(\sigma_1^2 - \sigma_2^2) + (\mu_1 - \mu_2)^2}{2\sigma_2^2}&lt;br>
}&lt;br>
$$&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="step-1-比值形式">Step 1. 比值形式&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
\frac{P(x)}{Q(x)} = \frac{\sigma_2}{\sigma_1} \exp \left[ \frac{\sigma_1^2(x - \mu_2)^2 - \sigma_2^2(x - \mu_1)^2}{2\sigma_1^2\sigma_2^2} \right]&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>因此&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
\log \frac{P(x)}{Q(x)} = \ln \frac{\sigma_2}{\sigma_1}&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>\frac{(\sigma_1^2 - \sigma_2^2)x^2 + (2\sigma_2^2\mu_1 - 2\sigma_1^2\mu_2)x + (\sigma_1^2\mu_2^2 - \mu_1^2\sigma_2^2)}{2\sigma_1^2\sigma_2^2}&lt;br>
$$&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="step-2-逐项积分">Step 2. 逐项积分&lt;/h2>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>二次项&lt;/strong>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
\int P(x) (\sigma_1^2 - \sigma_2^2) x^2 , dx&lt;br>
= (\sigma_1^2 - \sigma_2^2) \mathbb{E}[x^2]&lt;br>
= (\sigma_1^2 - \sigma_2^2)(\mu_1^2 + \sigma_1^2) \equiv A&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>山坡羊 自警</title><link>https://jzjizhe.github.io/literature/%E5%B1%B1%E5%9D%A1%E7%BE%8A-%E8%87%AA%E8%AD%A6/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Aug 2025 12:02:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://jzjizhe.github.io/literature/%E5%B1%B1%E5%9D%A1%E7%BE%8A-%E8%87%AA%E8%AD%A6/</guid><description>&lt;p>[元 乔吉]&lt;br>
